# AI Context (token-disciplined)

Project: Go `fmt-table` dynamic renderer.

Core behavior to preserve:
- Header/rows with aligned columns.
- Session persistence at `~/.cache/fmt-table/state.json`.
- Append + redraw workflow in interactive terminals.
- Explicit input required (`--title-row` and/or `--row`).

Compatibility stance:
- Accept legacy flags (`-b1`, `-s`, `-F`) as non-breaking no-ops.

Token efficiency rules:
- Keep under ~160 words.
- Only track active behavior constraints and immediate roadmap.
- Archive finalized decisions in `.ai_history`.
